title: Deshaun Meets With The NFL
description:
Field and the NFL Live Crew discuss the NFL and Deshaun Watson meeting today for their investigation, the Dolphins outlook after a busy offseason, did the Chiefs do enough to keep up with the rest of the AFC West, RC’s top 5 Jamar Chase CB matchups, and Get That Bag with Swagu.
